### Test Settlement Estimator Endpoint

### 1. Login to get access token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### 2. Get Settlement Estimator (for all meters owned by prosumer)
GET http://localhost:3000/energy/settlement-estimator
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 3. Get Settlement Estimator for specific meter
GET http://localhost:3000/energy/settlement-estimator?meterId=METER001
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

